{"tid":922940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個酒品唔好嘅例子","createTime":"2018-11-30T20:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T15:32:37.000Z","uid":24536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b480054176cdcab8def1a6c07dd81c5e10530c27","tid":922940,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:05:20.000Z","msg":"酒品唔好人品都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋下磚先<br />\n<br />\n咁啱又就到聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醒起有次見到個唔識嘅人喺朋友嘅聖誕party走去周圍撩人飲酒<br />\n結果喺到發酒癲鬧曬啲人 三唔識七咁都俾佢鬧到好似害佢全家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後當然俾人踢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後大家發覺佢做保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n心諗佢平時點做生意<br />\n<br />\n又聽過有啲狗公飲到醉曬自爆屌過自己兄弟條女<br />\n即時打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8e889cc20b8770e4151f700fc1ebd6662ddd14","tid":922940,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:05:45.000Z","msg":"有無啲癲啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5808610aed326f659d482b924ecd05ff3b0124e3","tid":922940,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:07:49.000Z","msg":"飲少少就扮醉開始博懵亂咁摸亂咁錫人 做晒平時唔會做但最想做嘅嘢又唔畀錢又要人送返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁憎條契弟"},{"pid":"b1f47825d0d7fac10880916209228bab47dd7604","tid":922940,"uid":24536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T20:07:49.000Z","msg":"見過有人喺發爛炸潑人啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f5d6cd0909d8101e57c883f056e0bedd08d9f8","tid":922940,"uid":141994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T21:05:07.000Z","msg":"周圍走唔受控制<br />\n我個fd試過跳落樓下露台<br />\n嚇死我地<br />\n<br />\n同埋情緒失控講ex呢啲又係好煩"},{"pid":"5c82e65514abb722140c17d02a2f75605b495649","tid":922940,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f5d6cd0909d8101e57c883f056e0bedd08d9f8","tid":922940,"uid":141994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T21:05:07.000Z","msg":"周圍走唔受控制<br />\n我個fd試過跳落樓下露台<br />\n嚇死我地<br />\n<br />\n同埋情緒失控講ex呢啲又係好煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"痴線個露台幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9ac7914b35d4ca6d7338f1906a95058e196ffe","tid":922940,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"男嘅 狗公上身 摸手摸腳搭膊攬腰 <br />\n女嘅 叫春喊苦喊忽<br />\n通用 唔飲得格硬黎 嘔到一地都係 <br />\n同埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚帶錢出黎飲酒</span></span><br />\n大家都約好出黎<br />\n出黎拎定錢好難咩<br />\n宜家又有payme轉數數<br />\n又乜撚都唔識用<br />\n飲到咁上下就醉到比唔到錢<br />\n屌你老母閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf45a2d0c055987e1b67fb88b67cf50b51da98b","tid":922940,"uid":24536,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1e9ac7914b35d4ca6d7338f1906a95058e196ffe","tid":922940,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"男嘅 狗公上身 摸手摸腳搭膊攬腰 <br />\n女嘅 叫春喊苦喊忽<br />\n通用 唔飲得格硬黎 嘔到一地都係 <br />\n同埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚帶錢出黎飲酒</span></span><br />\n大家都約好出黎<br />\n出黎拎定錢好難咩<br />\n宜家又有payme轉數數<br />\n又乜撚都唔識用<br />\n飲到咁上下就醉到比唔到錢<br />\n屌你老母閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁佢直頭唔飲酒都人品唔好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9893b3f40f921154ac77948332ec451b090bc448","tid":922940,"uid":21961,